code: @Test public void testHome() {     ResponseEntity<String> entity = this.restTemplate.getForEntity("/", String.class).     assertThat(entity.getStatusCode()).isEqualTo(HttpStatus.OK).     assertThat(entity.getBody()).contains("<title>Static"). }

@Test public void testCss() {     ResponseEntity<String> entity = this.restTemplate.getForEntity("/webjars/bootstrap/3.0.3/css/bootstrap.min.css", String.class).     assertThat(entity.getStatusCode()).isEqualTo(HttpStatus.OK).     assertThat(entity.getBody()).contains("body").     assertThat(entity.getHeaders().getContentType()).isEqualTo(MediaType.valueOf("text/css")). }
